{"tid":2462680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"H&M、Nike抵制新疆棉花的背後 中國版的「種植莊園奴隸」","createTime":"2021-03-26T07:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T07:43:26.000Z","uid":294518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48f34e767f6a17d1056e166d1c092a05233a4cbf","tid":2462680,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"H&amp;M、Nike抵制新疆棉花的背後 中國版的「種植莊園奴隸」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3dbfQZsmhlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3dbfQZsmhlE&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ggy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=7581eb63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3dbfQZsmhlE</a>"},{"pid":"6d75876d3c575a66edbfd5ab81d4518e1182de2f","tid":2462680,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aad8a16aa9933e7fb125be7b45d0152747e947","tid":2462680,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:02:10.000Z","msg":"普通新疆棉農只能高價從外地請人採摘，只有天氣預報有降雪時，為了趕時間才會使用機械採摘；<br />\n<br />\n但是新疆建設兵團由於有大量關押人員，強迫他們去地理摘棉花就是順利成章的事，這也是新疆建設兵團優質棉花成本低根源；<br />\n<br />\n這也是七匹狼等中資品牌喜歡與新疆兵團合作的原因，京東自營里也有很多在銷售產品！"},{"pid":"7dc4d737dc6a59e8fecafd24e4915d3dceaf91d5","tid":2462680,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"2019年時新疆每摘一公斤棉花，大約給2元人民幣的工資，平均每噸棉花人工成本為2000元，而新疆無雜質棉花出售價約為15000元，成本佔13.33%左右；<br />\n<br />\n即使這樣很多新疆棉農依然願意高價請人採摘，因為人工棉花確實很乾淨！機械採摘既會導致大量浪費（地上基本上散一層），又有很多雜質，根本賣不上價格！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1375266639277563909?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1375266639277563909%3Fs%3D20&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ggy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=6d3f012c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1375266639277563909%3Fs%3D20&h=acc403a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1375266639277563909?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"8683d7dbaeb1f3d558441ec30d6fd86c0e9abfbf","tid":2462680,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"每年9-11月，四川、河南、安徽、陝西等地農民都會有大批人去新疆摘棉花，中共還專門組織了火車專列！<br />\n<br />\n一朵棉花平均5克，一人一天至少可摘100-200公斤，對應的就是一天需要彎腰1萬-3萬次腰，一天下來就像被腰斬了一樣，渾身疼的沒法辦法！<br />\n<br />\n而且棉花殼也會經常把手划破，導致手指全是倒刺！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1375264888189190146?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1375264888189190146%3Fs%3D20&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Ggy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=c042c275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaijingxiang%2Fstatus%2F1375264888189190146%3Fs%3D20&h=018d468c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/caijingxiang/status/1375264888189190146?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"c5ed1d8708c3411a3209af61180370f33d2b4b07","tid":2462680,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"現代奴隸"},{"pid":"e4a2d7b9be9c7eec7d6eeddb19a6d68b18c8a3e3","tid":2462680,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾支那所謂既平就係因為奴隸制度，只係其他發達國家隻眼開隻眼閉，因為佢哋係得益者，當佢係非洲下等國家唔理，不過當支那想平起平坐既時候就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d455bbc6ddf8f7aac90981f0040ce0cca613bd37","tid":2462680,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a2d7b9be9c7eec7d6eeddb19a6d68b18c8a3e3","tid":2462680,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾支那所謂既平就係因為奴隸制度，只係其他發達國家隻眼開隻眼閉，因為佢哋係得益者，當佢係非洲下等國家唔理，不過當支那想平起平坐既時候就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"未發展國可以接受<br />\n但你是世界列強國 就唔可以咁玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}